Hey everyone,

I made this Function a while ago, it could or couldn't be useful but here it is anyway :D

[CODE]Finds the color, if not, uses a tolerance riser[/CODE]
[CODE]Function ClickMMColor(Color :integer; MaxTol : Integer): Boolean;
Var Tol : integer;

Begin
 for Tol:= 0 to MaxTol do
Begin
 Result:= FindColorSpiralTolerance(x,y,Color,574,8,724,157,Tol);
  if(Result)then
      Clickmouse(x,y,1);
        Wait(500+random(10/2*55/5*2));  
        Flag;
      Wait(101+random(6/2*12/5*6));  
    Exit;
  end;
end;[/CODE]


Replace Clickmouse and Flag to whichever Mouse/Flag Function you wish to use.


Cheers,
